UML:TaggedValue.value: This is the functional view of the Instant Mobility System. Components are organized in subsystems, each subsystem has its own package, the main subsystem is the "Multi-Modal Mobility" (goods and travellers). For each subsystem there is: - A main component diagram showing the subsystem internals. - A public interface diagram showing how the subsystem is connected to the outside world (actors and others sub-systems). See the "Multi-Modal Mobility" subsystem as example.
